  "limitations": [
    "The current producer graph has no registered PHP, browser, asset, or deployable site producers.",
    "The deterministic process-control corpus uses a TCP-listening Haxe protocol test double; real Haxe wait output parity is covered by SDK-040.",
    "The SDK-owned WordPress provider's generated Compose syntax and controlled process lifecycle are locally tested, and its exact image pair is separately runtime tested by SDK-090; this gate does not start that pair through wphx dev or mount and install a generated site because target producers are not registered.",
    "Post-publication reload requests are locally tested, but a real browser reload transport and the optional Next.js adapter are not implemented.",
    "Windows, network filesystems, abrupt host failure, installed consumers, package publication, and production deployment remain untested."
